			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=3>
				Well man in my opinion it doesnt really matter what you wear or what weapon you use at that level. Wear cloth stuff cause its cheap, at your level I got a runed totem staff. Its a 2 hand blunt staff with ok damage and it gives you mana and hit points. You can buy one for 10pp or so off a player. DO NOT buy it from the store! I payed like 80pp to a vendor for mine, big mistake =) <br>   Eventually my man you wont even use your melee weapons. I have steins. When you get to a certain point it is just not effective to bash along side your pet! Tesch Mas Gnolls that I fight now hit for like 52dmg. When you only have 500 hit points you die fast. Us mages use earth pets to hold our monsters in one spot while we STAND BACK and nuke them with spell. Why would we want to stand and hit them for 18dmg when we can get back and cast for 176dmg?  <br>   I guess just pick a cheap weapon and use it until you get your big nuke spells and like lvl 16. Good luck! <br>  <br>  <br> Sachator Hammet <br> Level 27 Erudite Magician		

